<div class="card portal-welcome">
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row g-3 align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="portal-welcome-badge">Department of Electrical Engineering, NTU</div>
        <h1><%= @user_configuration.dashboard_title %></h1>
        <p class="lead">集中管理 Slurm 作業、互動式桌面、檔案存取與常用工具，讓叢集工作流程更直接。</p>
        <div class="portal-welcome-meta">登入後可直接使用儀表板中的常用工具，並從系統狀態頁查看目前叢集狀態。</div>
        <div class="portal-welcome-actions">
          <%= link_to t('dashboard.files'), files_path(fs: 'fs', filepath: Dir.home), class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
          <%= link_to t('dashboard.my_interactive_sessions'), batch_connect_sessions_path, class: 'btn btn-outline-primary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="portal-welcome-stat">
          <div class="portal-welcome-stat-label">Portal Access</div>
          <div class="portal-welcome-stat-value"><%= @user.name %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="portal-welcome-stat mt-3">
          <div class="portal-welcome-stat-label">Cluster</div>
          <div class="portal-welcome-stat-value">NTU EE Core HPC</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
